-- White Mountains to Buy Runoff Insurers From PICO for $17 Million
-- B y   S t e v e n   N o r t o n
-- 2012-06-20T20:39:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-20/white-mountains-to-buy-runoff-insurers-from-pico-for-17-million.html
White Mountains Insurance Group Ltd. (WTM) 
agreed to buy two units from  PICO Holdings Inc. (PICO)  that ceased
writing new policies in the 1990s.  White Mountains will pay about $17 million for Physicians
Insurance of Ohio and Citation Insurance Co., assuming assets
and liabilities from the so-called runoff companies, the buyer
said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Steven Norton in New York at 
 Snorton7@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
